{"type":"message","id":"1def00c2","parentId":"30e45c0e","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:00:14.067Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0e7d4856d1a2495bb1723f7a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk.Web\">\n\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net10.0</TargetFramework>\n    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>\n    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>\n    <RootNamespace>Tianyou.Web</RootNamespace>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <PackageReference Include=\"MudBlazor\" Version=\"7.8.0\" />\n    <PackageReference Include=\"Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components.WebAssembly.Server\" Version=\"10.0.0-preview.1.*\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <ProjectReference Include=\"..\\Tianyou.Domain\\Tianyou.Domain.csproj\" />\n    <ProjectReference Include=\"..\\Tianyou.Infrastructure\\Tianyou.Infrastructure.csproj\" />\n    <ProjectReference Include=\"..\\Tianyou.LowCode.Engine\\Tianyou.LowCode.Engine.csproj\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n\n</Project>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774224014059}}
{"type":"message","id":"567528c3","parentId":"1def00c2","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:01:07.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我将创建一个独立的Blazor组件用于流程设计器，可以嵌入到现有的Tianyou.Web项目中。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_82ebc466bb994f879fd02442","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/web/Tianyou.Web/Components/WorkflowDesigner.razor","content":"@inject HttpClient Http\n@inject NavigationManager NavigationManager\n@inject IDialogService DialogService\n\n<MudCard Elevation=\"2\">\n    <MudCardHeader>\n        <CardHeaderContent>\n            <MudText Typo=\"Typo.h5\">流程设计器</MudText>\n        </CardHeaderContent>\n        <CardHeaderActions>\n            <MudButton Variant=\"Variant.Filled\" Color=\"Color.Primary\" OnClick=\"SaveWorkflow\">\n                <MudIcon Icon=\"@Icons.Material.Filled.Save\" Class=\"mr-2\" />\n                保存\n            </MudButton>\n            <MudButton Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\" Color=\"Color.Secondary\" OnClick=\"ValidateWorkflow\">\n                <MudIcon Icon=\"@Icons.Material.Filled.CheckCircle\" Class=\"mr-2\" />\n                验证\n            </MudButton>\n            <MudButton Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\" OnClick=\"PublishWorkflow\">\n                <MudIcon Icon=\"@Icons.Material.Filled.Publish\" Class=\"mr-2\" />\n                发布\n            </MudButton>\n        </CardHeaderActions>\n    </MudCardHeader>\n    \n    <MudCardContent>\n        <MudGrid>\n            <MudItem xs=\"12\" md=\"3\">\n                <MudPaper Elevation=\"1\" Class=\"pa-2\" Style=\"height: 600px; overflow-y: auto;\">\n                    <MudText Typo=\"Typo.h6\" Class=\"mb-2\">流程信息</MudText>\n                    \n                    <MudTextField @bind-Value=\"workflow.Name\" \n                                  Label=\"流程名称\" \n                                  Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\"\n                                  Class=\"mb-2\" />\n                    \n                    <MudTextField @bind-Value=\"workflow.Code\" \n                                  Label=\"流程编码\" \n                                  Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\"\n                                  Class=\"mb-2\" />\n                    \n                    <MudSelect @bind-Value=\"workflow.Category\" \n                               Label=\"流程分类\" \n                               Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\"\n                               Class=\"mb-2\">\n                        <MudSelectItem Value=\"@(\"人事审批\")\">人事审批</MudSelectItem>\n                        <MudSelectItem Value=\"@(\"财务审批\")\">财务审批</MudSelectItem>\n                        <MudSelectItem Value=\"@(\"行政审批\")\">行政审批</MudSelectItem>\n                        <MudSelectItem Value=\"@(\"其他\")\">其他</MudSelectItem>\n                    </MudSelect>\n                    \n                    <MudTextArea @bind-Value=\"workflow.Description\" \n                                 Label=\"流程描述\" \n                                 Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\"\n                                 Rows=\"3\"\n                                 Class=\"mb-2\" />\n                    \n                    <MudDivider Class=\"my-4\" />\n                    \n                    <MudText Typo=\"Typo.subtitle1\" Class=\"mb-2\">审批节点</MudText>\n                    \n                    @foreach (var node in workflow.ApprovalNodes)\n                    {\n                        <MudChip TData=\"string\" \n                                 Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\" \n                                 OnClick=\"@(() => EditNode(node))\"\n                                 Class=\"ma-1\">\n                            @node.NodeName\n                        </MudChip>\n                    }\n                    \n                    <MudButton Variant=\"Variant.Text\" \n                               Color=\"Color.Primary\" \n                               OnClick=\"AddNode\"\n                               FullWidth=\"true\">\n                        <MudIcon Icon=\"@Icons.Material.Filled.Add\" Class=\"mr-1\" />\n                        添加节点\n                    </MudButton>\n                </MudPaper>\n            </MudItem>\n            \n            <MudItem xs=\"12\" md=\"6\">\n                <MudPaper Elevation=\"1\" Class=\"pa-2\" Style=\"height: 600px; position: relative;\">\n                    <div id=\"bpmn-canvas\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\"></div>\n                </MudPaper>\n            </MudItem>\n            \n            <MudItem xs=\"12\" md=\"3\">\n                <MudPaper Elevation=\"1\" Class=\"pa-2\" Style=\"height: 600px; overflow-y: auto;\">\n                    <MudText Typo=\"Typo.h6\" Class=\"mb-2\">属性面板</MudText>\n                    \n                    @if (selectedNode != null)\n                    {\n                        <MudTextField @bind-Value=\"selectedNode.NodeName\" \n                                      Label=\"节点名称\" \n                                      Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\"\n                                      Class=\"mb-2\" />\n                        \n                        <MudSelect @bind-Value=\"selectedNode.ApprovalType\" \n                                   Label=\"审批类型\" \n                                   Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\"\n                                   Class=\"mb-2\">\n                            <MudSelectItem Value=\"@((ApprovalType)0)\">或签</MudSelectItem>\n                            <MudSelectItem Value=\"@((ApprovalType)1)\">会签</MudSelectItem>\n                            <MudSelectItem Value=\"@((ApprovalType)2)\">顺序审批</MudSelectItem>\n                        </MudSelect>\n                        \n                        <MudNumericField @bind-Value=\"selectedNode.TimeoutHours\" \n                                         Label=\"超时时间(小时)\" \n                                         Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\"\n                                         Min=\"1\"\n                                         Max=\"720\"\n                                         Class=\"mb-2\" />\n                        \n                        <MudSwitch @bind-Value=\"selectedNode.AllowTransfer\" \n                                   Label=\"允许转办\" \n                                   Class=\"mb-2\" />\n                        \n                        <MudSwitch @bind-Value=\"selectedNode.AllowDelegate\" \n                                   Label=\"允许委派\" \n                                   Class=\"mb-2\" />\n                        \n                        <MudDivider Class=\"my-3\" />\n                        \n                        <MudText Typo=\"Typo.subtitle2\">审批人</MudText>\n                        \n                        <MudButton Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\" \n                                   Size=\"Size.Small\"\n                                   OnClick=\"@(() => SelectApprovers(selectedNode))\"\n                                   Class=\"mt-2\">\n                            选择审批人\n                        </MudButton>\n                        \n                        <MudButton Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\" \n                                   Size=\"Size.Small\"\n                                   OnClick=\"@(() => SelectApproverRoles(selectedNode))\"\n                                   Class=\"mt-2 ml-2\">\n                            选择角色\n                        </MudButton>\n                    }\n                    else\n                    {\n                        <MudAlert Severity=\"Severity.Info\">请选择一个节点进行编辑</MudAlert>\n                    }\n                </MudPaper>\n            </MudItem>\n        </MudGrid>\n    </MudCardContent>\n</MudCard>\n\n<MudDialog @bind-IsOpen=\"showNodeDialog\">\n    <TitleContent>\n        <MudText Typo=\"Typo.h6\">添加审批节点</MudText>\n    </TitleContent>\n    <DialogContent>\n        <MudTextField @bind-Value=\"newNodeName\" \n                      Label=\"节点名称\" \n                      Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\" />\n        \n        <MudSelect @bind-Value=\"newNodeType\" \n                   Label=\"节点类型\" \n                   Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\"\n                   Class=\"mt-2\">\n            <MudSelectItem Value=\"@(\"审批\")\">审批节点</MudSelectItem>\n            <MudSelectItem Value=\"@(\"抄送\")\">抄送节点</MudSelectItem>\n            <MudSelectItem Value=\"@(\"条件\")\">条件分支</MudSelectItem>\n        </MudSelect>\n    </DialogContent>\n    <DialogActions>\n        <MudButton OnClick=\"() => showNodeDialog = false\">取消</MudButton>\n        <MudButton Color=\"Color.Primary\" OnClick=\"ConfirmAddNode\">确定</MudButton>\n    </DialogActions>\n</MudDialog>\n\n@code {\n    [Parameter]\n    public string? WorkflowId { get; set; }\n    \n    private WorkflowDefinition workflow = new WorkflowDefinition();\n    private ApprovalNode? selectedNode;\n    private bool showNodeDialog = false;\n    private string newNodeName = \"\";\n    private string newNodeType = \"审批\";\n    \n    protected override async Task OnInitializedAsync()\n    {\n        if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(WorkflowId))\n        {\n            await LoadWorkflow(WorkflowId);\n        }\n    }\n    \n    protected override async Task OnAfterRenderAsync(bool firstRender)\n    {\n        if (firstRender)\n        {\n            await InitializeBpmnModeler();\n        }\n    }\n    \n    private async Task LoadWorkflow(string id)\n    {\n        try\n        {\n            var response = await Http.GetFromJsonAsync<WorkflowDefinition>(\n                $\"http://localhost:5005/api/workflow/{id}\");\n            \n            if (response != null)\n            {\n                workflow = response;\n                await LoadBpmnDiagram(workflow.BpmnXml);\n            }\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            Console.WriteLine($\"加载流程失败: {ex.Message}\");\n        }\n    }\n    \n    private async Task InitializeBpmnModeler()\n    {\n        // 这里需要通过JS互操作调用bpmn-js\n        // 实际实现中需要引入bpmn-js库\n        await JS.InvokeVoidAsync(\"initializeBpmnModeler\", \"bpmn-canvas\");\n    }\n    \n    private async Task LoadBpmnDiagram(string bpmnXml)\n    {\n        if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(bpmnXml))\n        {\n            await JS.InvokeVoidAsync(\"loadBpmnDiagram\", bpmnXml);\n        }\n    }\n    \n    private async Task SaveWorkflow()\n    {\n        try\n        {\n            // 获取BPMN XML\n            workflow.BpmnXml = await JS.InvokeAsync<string>(\"getBpmnXml\");\n            \n            var response = await Http.PostAsJsonAsync(\n                \"http://localhost:5005/api/workflow\", \n                workflow);\n            \n            if (response.IsSuccessStatusCode)\n            {\n                DialogService.Show<SuccessDialog>(\"保存成功\");\n            }\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            Console.WriteLine($\"保存失败: {ex.Message}\");\n        }\n    }\n    \n    private async Task ValidateWorkflow()\n    {\n        try\n        {\n            var bpmnXml = await JS.InvokeAsync<string>(\"getBpmnXml\");\n            var response = await Http.PostAsJsonAsync(\n                \"http://localhost:5005/api/workflow/validate\",\n                new { BpmnXml = bpmnXml });\n            \n            if (response.IsSuccessStatusCode)\n            {\n                var result = await response.Content.ReadFromJsonAsync<ValidationResult>();\n                if (result?.IsValid == true)\n                {\n                    DialogService.Show<SuccessDialog>(\"验证通过\");\n                }\n                else\n                {\n                    DialogService.Show<ErrorDialog>(\"验证失败: \" + string.Join(\", \", result?.Errors ?? new List<string>()));\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            Console.WriteLine($\"验证失败: {ex.Message}\");\n        }\n    }\n    \n    private async Task PublishWorkflow()\n    {\n        try\n        {\n            var response = await Http.PostAsync(\n                $\"http://localhost:5005/api/workflow/{workflow.Id}/publish\", null);\n            \n            if (response.IsSuccessStatusCode)\n            {\n                DialogService.Show<SuccessDialog>(\"发布成功\");\n            }\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            Console.WriteLine($\"发布失败: {ex.Message}\");\n        }\n    }\n    \n    private void AddNode()\n    {\n        newNodeName = \"\";\n        newNodeType = \"审批\";\n        showNodeDialog = true;\n    }\n    \n    private void ConfirmAddNode()\n    {\n        if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(newNodeName))\n        {\n            var node = new ApprovalNode\n            {\n                NodeId = Guid.NewGuid().ToString(),\n                NodeName = newNodeName,\n                ApprovalType = newNodeType == \"审批\" ? ApprovalType.OrSign : ApprovalType.AndSign,\n                TimeoutHours = 72\n            };\n            \n            workflow.ApprovalNodes.Add(node);\n            selectedNode = node;\n        }\n        \n        showNodeDialog = false;\n    }\n    \n    private void EditNode(ApprovalNode node)\n    {\n        selectedNode = node;\n        StateHasChanged();\n    }\n    \n    private void SelectApprovers(ApprovalNode node)\n    {\n        // TODO: 打开用户选择对话框\n    }\n    \n    private void SelectApproverRoles(ApprovalNode node)\n    {\n        // TODO: 打开角色选择对话框\n    }\n    \n    [Inject] private IJSRuntime JS { get; set; } = null!;\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":279,"output":2658,"cacheRead":29440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32377,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774224014068}}
