{"type":"message","id":"031b3034","parentId":"a0942e68","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:01:37.498Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建任务列表和审批页面的Blazor组件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_539f96d4c0ee463b88521e51","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/web/Tianyou.Web/Components/PendingTasks.razor","content":"@inject HttpClient Http\n@inject NavigationManager NavigationManager\n@inject IDialogService DialogService\n\n<MudCard Elevation=\"2\">\n    <MudCardHeader>\n        <CardHeaderContent>\n            <MudText Typo=\"Typo.h5\">\n                <MudIcon Icon=\"@Icons.Material.Filled.PendingActions\" Class=\"mr-2\" />\n                待办任务\n            </MudText>\n        </CardHeaderContent>\n        <CardHeaderActions>\n            <MudTextField @bind-Value=\"searchKeyword\" \n                          Placeholder=\"搜索...\" \n                          Adornment=\"Adornment.Start\"\n                          AdornmentIcon=\"@Icons.Material.Filled.Search\"\n                          Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\"\n                          Margin=\"Margin.Dense\"\n                          Style=\"width: 250px;\" />\n        </CardHeaderActions>\n    </MudCardHeader>\n    \n    <MudCardContent>\n        @if (tasks == null)\n        {\n            <MudProgressLinear Color=\"Color.Primary\" Indeterminate=\"true\" />\n        }\n        else if (tasks.Items.Count == 0)\n        {\n            <MudAlert Severity=\"Severity.Info\" Class=\"mt-4\">\n                暂无待办任务\n            </MudAlert>\n        }\n        else\n        {\n            <MudTable Items=\"@tasks.Items\" \n                      Hover=\"true\" \n                      Striped=\"true\"\n                      Elevation=\"0\">\n                <HeaderContent>\n                    <MudTh><MudTableSortLabel SortBy=\"new Func<WorkflowTask, object>(x => x.TaskName)\">任务名称</MudTableSortLabel></MudTh>\n                    <MudTh>流程名称</MudTh>\n                    <MudTh>发起人</MudTh>\n                    <MudTh>到达时间</MudTh>\n                    <MudTh>到期时间</MudTh>\n                    <MudTh>优先级</MudTh>\n                    <MudTh Style=\"width: 150px;\">操作</MudTh>\n                </HeaderContent>\n                <RowTemplate>\n                    <MudTd DataLabel=\"任务名称\">\n                        <MudText Typo=\"Typo.body1\">@context.TaskName</MudText>\n                        <MudText Typo=\"Typo.caption\" Color=\"Color.Secondary\">@context.InstanceId</MudText>\n                    </MudTd>\n                    <MudTd DataLabel=\"流程名称\">\n                        @GetWorkflowName(context.InstanceId)\n                    </MudTd>\n                    <MudTd DataLabel=\"发起人\">\n                        @GetInitiatorName(context.InstanceId)\n                    </MudTd>\n                    <MudTd DataLabel=\"到达时间\">\n                        @context.CreateTime.ToString(\"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm\")\n                    </MudTd>\n                    <MudTd DataLabel=\"到期时间\">\n                        @if (context.DueDate.HasValue)\n                        {\n                            var remaining = context.DueDate.Value - DateTime.UtcNow;\n                            @if (remaining.TotalHours < 0)\n                            {\n                                <MudChip TData=\"string\" Color=\"Color.Error\" Size=\"Size.Small\">已超时</MudChip>\n                            }\n                            else if (remaining.TotalHours < 24)\n                            {\n                                <MudChip TData=\"string\" Color=\"Color.Warning\" Size=\"Size.Small\">@((int)remaining.TotalHours)小时</MudChip>\n                            }\n                            else\n                            {\n                                <MudText>@context.DueDate.Value.ToString(\"yyyy-MM-dd\")</MudText>\n                            }\n                        }\n                    </MudTd>\n                    <MudTd DataLabel=\"优先级\">\n                        @switch (context.Priority)\n                        {\n                            case 1:\n                                <MudChip TData=\"string\" Color=\"Color.Error\" Size=\"Size.Small\">紧急</MudChip>\n                                break;\n                            case 2:\n                                <MudChip TData=\"string\" Color=\"Color.Warning\" Size=\"Size.Small\">高</MudChip>\n                                break;\n                            default:\n                                <MudChip TData=\"string\" Color=\"Color.Default\" Size=\"Size.Small\">普通</MudChip>\n                                break;\n                        }\n                    </MudTd>\n                    <MudTd DataLabel=\"操作\">\n                        <MudButtonGroup Variant=\"Variant.Outlined\" Size=\"Size.Small\">\n                            <MudButton Color=\"Color.Primary\" OnClick=\"@(() => HandleTask(context))\">\n                                处理\n                            </MudButton>\n                            <MudButton Color=\"Color.Secondary\" OnClick=\"@(() => TransferTask(context))\">\n                                转办\n                            </MudButton>\n                        </MudButtonGroup>\n                    </MudTd>\n                </RowTemplate>\n                <PagerContent>\n                    <MudTablePager PageSizeOptions=\"new int[] { 10, 25, 50, 100 }\" />\n                </PagerContent>\n            </MudTable>\n        }\n    </MudCardContent>\n</MudCard>\n\n@code {\n    [Parameter]\n    public string UserId { get; set; } = \"current-user\";\n    \n    private PagedResult<WorkflowTask>? tasks;\n    private string searchKeyword = \"\";\n    private Dictionary<string, WorkflowInstance> instanceCache = new();\n    \n    protected override async Task OnInitializedAsync()\n    {\n        await LoadTasks();\n    }\n    \n    private async Task LoadTasks()\n    {\n        try\n        {\n            tasks = await Http.GetFromJsonAsync<PagedResult<WorkflowTask>>(\n                $\"http://localhost:5005/api/workflow/tasks/pending/{UserId}?page=1&pageSize=20\");\n            \n            // 预加载实例信息\n            if (tasks != null)\n            {\n                foreach (var task in tasks.Items)\n                {\n                    if (!instanceCache.ContainsKey(task.InstanceId))\n                    {\n                        var instance = await Http.GetFromJsonAsync<WorkflowInstance>(\n                            $\"http://localhost:5005/api/workflow/instances/{task.InstanceId}\");\n                        \n                        if (instance != null)\n                        {\n                            instanceCache[task.InstanceId] = instance;\n                        }\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            Console.WriteLine($\"加载待办任务失败: {ex.Message}\");\n        }\n    }\n    \n    private string GetWorkflowName(string instanceId)\n    {\n        if (instanceCache.TryGetValue(instanceId, out var instance))\n        {\n            return instance.Name;\n        }\n        return instanceId;\n    }\n    \n    private string GetInitiatorName(string instanceId)\n    {\n        if (instanceCache.TryGetValue(instanceId, out var instance))\n        {\n            return instance.InitiatorName;\n        }\n        return \"未知\";\n    }\n    \n    private void HandleTask(WorkflowTask task)\n    {\n        NavigationManager.NavigateTo($\"/workflow/task/{task.Id}\");\n    }\n    \n    private async Task TransferTask(WorkflowTask task)\n    {\n        var parameters = new DialogParameters\n        {\n            [\"TaskId\"] = task.Id,\n            [\"FromUserId\"] = UserId\n        };\n        \n        var dialog = await DialogService.ShowAsync<TransferDialog>(\"转办任务\", parameters);\n        var result = await dialog.Result;\n        \n        if (result != null && !result.Canceled)\n        {\n            await LoadTasks();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2720,"output":1561,"cacheRead":29696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33977,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774224068037}}
