{"type":"message","id":"5aeea3a2","parentId":"f063e7cd","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:04:10.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"更新Program.cs以初始化示例数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5595418320b64a52aa98eb88","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"// 自动迁移数据库\nusing (var scope = app.Services.CreateScope())\n{\n    var context = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService<WorkflowDbContext>();\n    context.Database.EnsureCreated();\n    \n    // 初始化示例数据\n    WorkflowDataSeeder.Seed(context);\n}","oldText":"// 自动迁移数据库\nusing (var scope = app.Services.CreateScope())\n{\n    var context = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService<WorkflowDbContext>();\n    context.Database.EnsureCreated();\n}","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/services/Tianyou.WorkflowService/Program.cs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1915,"output":149,"cacheRead":39232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41296,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774224242832}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a1ede9a","parentId":"5aeea3a2","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:04:10.099Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5595418320b64a52aa98eb88","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/services/Tianyou.WorkflowService/Program.cs."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  64 using (var scope = app.Services.CreateScope())\n  65 {\n  66     var context = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService<WorkflowDbContext>();\n  67     context.Database.EnsureCreated();\n+ 68     \n+ 69     // 初始化示例数据\n+ 70     WorkflowDataSeeder.Seed(context);\n  68 }\n  69 \n  70 app.UseCors(\"AllowAll\");\n  71 app.MapControllers();\n     ...","firstChangedLine":68},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774224250076}}
{"type":"message","id":"4fd3e3d8","parentId":"0a1ede9a","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:04:40.806Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建API测试文档和启动脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_24ac036343694c80a4ef0200","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/services/Tianyou.WorkflowService/API_TEST_GUIDE.md","content":"# 工作流服务 API 测试指南\n\n## 基础URL\n```\nhttp://localhost:5005\n```\n\n## 1. 流程定义管理\n\n### 1.1 创建流程定义\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"name\": \"请假审批流程\",\n  \"code\": \"LEAVE_APPROVAL\",\n  \"category\": \"人事审批\",\n  \"description\": \"员工请假审批流程\",\n  \"bpmnXml\": \"<?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"UTF-8\\\"?>...\",\n  \"approvalNodes\": [\n    {\n      \"nodeId\": \"Node_Manager\",\n      \"nodeName\": \"部门经理审批\",\n      \"approvalType\": 0,\n      \"approverRoleIds\": [\"manager\"],\n      \"timeoutHours\": 24\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 1.2 获取流程定义列表\n```http\nGET /api/workflow?page=1&pageSize=20&category=人事审批&status=1\n```\n\n### 1.3 获取单个流程定义\n```http\nGET /api/workflow/{id}\n```\n\n### 1.4 更新流程定义\n```http\nPUT /api/workflow/{id}\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"name\": \"更新后的流程名称\",\n  \"description\": \"更新描述\"\n}\n```\n\n### 1.5 发布流程定义\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/{id}/publish\n```\n\n### 1.6 验证流程定义\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/validate\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"bpmnXml\": \"<?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"UTF-8\\\"?>...\"\n}\n```\n\n### 1.7 删除流程定义\n```http\nDELETE /api/workflow/{id}\n```\n\n## 2. 流程实例管理\n\n### 2.1 启动流程实例\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/{definitionId}/start\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"initiatorId\": \"user001\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"leaveType\": \"事假\",\n    \"days\": 3,\n    \"reason\": \"个人事务\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 获取流程实例\n```http\nGET /api/workflow/instances/{instanceId}\n```\n\n### 2.3 获取流程实例列表\n```http\nGET /api/workflow/instances?page=1&pageSize=20&state=0&initiatorId=user001\n```\n\n### 2.4 挂起流程实例\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/instances/{instanceId}/suspend\n```\n\n### 2.5 恢复流程实例\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/instances/{instanceId}/resume\n```\n\n### 2.6 取消流程实例\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/instances/{instanceId}/cancel\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"reason\": \"取消原因\"\n}\n```\n\n## 3. 任务管理\n\n### 3.1 获取待办任务\n```http\nGET /api/workflow/tasks/pending/{userId}?page=1&pageSize=20\n```\n\n### 3.2 获取已办任务\n```http\nGET /api/workflow/tasks/completed/{userId}?page=1&pageSize=20\n```\n\n### 3.3 获取任务详情\n```http\nGET /api/workflow/tasks/{taskId}\n```\n\n### 3.4 认领任务\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/tasks/{taskId}/claim\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"userId\": \"user001\"\n}\n```\n\n## 4. 审批操作\n\n### 4.1 同意审批\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/tasks/{taskId}/approve\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"userId\": \"user001\",\n  \"comment\": \"同意，情况属实\"\n}\n```\n\n### 4.2 拒绝审批\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/tasks/{taskId}/reject\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"userId\": \"user001\",\n  \"comment\": \"拒绝，理由不足\"\n}\n```\n\n### 4.3 转办任务\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/tasks/{taskId}/transfer\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"fromUserId\": \"user001\",\n  \"toUserId\": \"user002\",\n  \"comment\": \"转办给更合适的审批人\"\n}\n```\n\n### 4.4 委派任务\n```http\nPOST /api/workflow/tasks/{taskId}/delegate\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"fromUserId\": \"user001\",\n  \"toUserId\": \"user002\",\n  \"comment\": \"委派处理\"\n}\n```\n\n### 4.5 获取审批记录\n```http\nGET /api/workflow/instances/{instanceId}/approval-records\n```\n\n## 5. 状态枚举\n\n### WorkflowStatus (流程状态)\n- 0: Draft (草稿)\n- 1: Published (已发布)\n- 2: Deprecated (已废弃)\n- 3: Archived (已归档)\n\n### WorkflowInstanceState (流程实例状态)\n- 0: Running (运行中)\n- 1: Suspended (已挂起)\n- 2: Completed (已完成)\n- 3: Cancelled (已取消)\n- 4: Faulted (错误)\n\n### TaskState (任务状态)\n- 0: Pending (待办)\n- 1: InProgress (进行中)\n- 2: Completed (已完成)\n- 3: Cancelled (已取消)\n- 4: Error (错误)\n\n### ApprovalType (审批类型)\n- 0: OrSign (或签 - 任一人通过即可)\n- 1: AndSign (会签 - 所有人都需通过)\n- 2: Sequential (顺序审批)\n\n### ApprovalAction (审批动作)\n- 0: Approve (同意)\n- 1: Reject (拒绝)\n- 2: Transfer (转办)\n- 3: Delegate (委派)\n- 4: Withdraw (撤回)\n- 5: Cancel (取消)\n\n## 6. Swagger文档\n访问 http://localhost:5005/swagger 查看完整的API文档\n\n## 7. Hangfire Dashboard\n访问 http://localhost:5005/hangfire 查看定时任务管理面板\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":244,"output":1433,"cacheRead":41088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42765,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774224250109}}
