{"type":"message","id":"0659604a","parentId":"5a3407e8","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:05:39.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有安装.NET SDK。让我创建一个部署说明文档和Dockerfile来解决这个问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_470ccae838a845709363c948","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/services/Tianyou.WorkflowService/README.md","content":"# 工作流服务部署指南\n\n## 环境要求\n\n- .NET 8.0 SDK\n- SQL Server (可选，默认使用SQLite)\n- Docker (可选)\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 方式1: 本地运行\n\n```bash\n# 1. 安装.NET 8.0 SDK\n# Ubuntu/Debian\nwget https://dot.net/v1/dotnet-install.sh -O dotnet-install.sh\nchmod +x dotnet-install.sh\n./dotnet-install.sh --channel 8.0\n\n# 添加到PATH\nexport DOTNET_ROOT=$HOME/.dotnet\nexport PATH=$PATH:$DOTNET_ROOT:$DOTNET_ROOT/tools\n\n# 2. 还原依赖\ncd services/Tianyou.WorkflowService\ndotnet restore\n\n# 3. 运行服务\n./start.sh\n```\n\n### 方式2: Docker运行\n\n```bash\n# 构建镜像\ndocker build -t tianyou-workflow:latest .\n\n# 运行容器\ndocker run -d \\\n  --name workflow-service \\\n  -p 5005:5005 \\\n  -e ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection=\"Server=host.docker.internal;Database=TianyouWorkflow;User=sa;Password=YourPassword123\" \\\n  tianyou-workflow:latest\n```\n\n### 方式3: Docker Compose\n\n```bash\n# 启动所有服务\ndocker-compose up -d\n\n# 查看日志\ndocker-compose logs -f workflow-service\n```\n\n## 配置说明\n\n### appsettings.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"ConnectionStrings\": {\n    \"DefaultConnection\": \"Server=localhost;Database=TianyouWorkflow;Trusted_Connection=true;MultipleActiveResultSets=true;TrustServerCertificate=true\"\n  },\n  \"Logging\": {\n    \"LogLevel\": {\n      \"Default\": \"Information\",\n      \"Microsoft\": \"Warning\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"Hangfire\": {\n    \"DashboardPath\": \"/hangfire\",\n    \"Authorization\": {\n      \"Enabled\": false\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 环境变量\n\n```bash\n# 数据库连接\nConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection=\"your-connection-string\"\n\n# 服务端口\nASPNETCORE_URLS=\"http://0.0.0.0:5005\"\n\n# 环境\nASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT=\"Production\"\n```\n\n## 数据库配置\n\n### SQLite (默认)\n无需额外配置，自动创建 `workflow.db` 文件\n\n### SQL Server\n```bash\nexport ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection=\"Server=localhost;Database=TianyouWorkflow;User=sa;Password=YourPassword\"\n```\n\n### PostgreSQL\n1. 安装Npgsql.EntityFrameworkCore.PostgreSQL包\n2. 修改Program.cs:\n```csharp\nbuilder.Services.AddDbContext<WorkflowDbContext>(options =>\n    options.UseNpgsql(connectionString));\n```\n\n## 生产环境建议\n\n### 1. 数据库优化\n- 使用SQL Server或PostgreSQL\n- 配置连接池\n- 启用数据库日志\n\n### 2. 安全配置\n- 启用HTTPS\n- 配置CORS策略\n- 启用Hangfire授权\n- 使用JWT认证\n\n### 3. 性能优化\n- 启用响应缓存\n- 配置输出缓存\n- 使用Redis缓存\n- 配置Hangfire持久化存储\n\n### 4. 监控\n- 配置健康检查\n- 启用Prometheus指标\n- 配置日志聚合\n- 设置告警规则\n\n## Hangfire配置\n\n### 使用SQL Server存储\n```csharp\nbuilder.Services.AddHangfire(config => config\n    .UseSqlServerStorage(connectionString));\n```\n\n### 启用授权\n```csharp\napp.UseHangfireDashboard(\"/hangfire\", new DashboardOptions\n{\n    Authorization = new[] { new MyAuthorizationFilter() }\n});\n```\n\n## 故障排查\n\n### 常见问题\n\n1. **端口被占用**\n```bash\n# 查找占用端口的进程\nlsof -i :5005\n# 结束进程\nkill -9 <PID>\n```\n\n2. **数据库连接失败**\n- 检查连接字符串\n- 确认数据库服务运行\n- 检查防火墙规则\n\n3. **依赖包冲突**\n```bash\n# 清理并重新构建\ndotnet clean\ndotnet restore\ndotnet build\n```\n\n## 性能测试\n\n```bash\n# 安装wrk\nsudo apt install wrk\n\n# 测试健康检查\nwrk -t4 -c100 -d30s http://localhost:5005/health\n\n# 测试API\nwrk -t4 -c100 -d30s -s post.lua http://localhost:5005/api/workflow\n```\n\n## 备份与恢复\n\n### 备份数据库\n```bash\n# SQL Server\nsqlcmd -S localhost -U sa -P password -Q \"BACKUP DATABASE [TianyouWorkflow] TO DISK='/backup/workflow.bak'\"\n\n# SQLite\ncp workflow.db workflow.db.backup\n```\n\n### 恢复数据库\n```bash\n# SQL Server\nsqlcmd -S localhost -U sa -P password -Q \"RESTORE DATABASE [TianyouWorkflow] FROM DISK='/backup/workflow.bak'\"\n```\n\n## 日志管理\n\n### 查看日志\n```bash\n# 实时日志\ntail -f logs/workflow-*.log\n\n# 搜索错误\ngrep -i error logs/workflow-*.log\n```\n\n### 日志轮转\n日志按天自动轮转，保留最近30天的日志\n\n## 更新与升级\n\n```bash\n# 拉取最新代码\ngit pull\n\n# 重新构建\ndotnet build --configuration Release\n\n# 重启服务\nsystemctl restart tianyou-workflow\n```\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":155,"output":1295,"cacheRead":43968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45418,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774224312246}}
